Generate changelogs from conventional commits.

Usage: changelogen [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  show      Show the next inferred version
  generate  Generate release block (writes with --write)
  release   Run full release (bump, changelog, tag creation optional in future)
  github    GitHub release synchronization only
  help      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --cwd <CWD>
          

  -v...
          Increase verbosity (-v, -vv, -vvv)

  -h, --help
          Print help

  -V, --version
          Print version
